title: 820-00165 MacBook Air 2017 water damage
message:
"PPBUS_G3H 8.6 V"
This implies SMC_RESET_L is good; why don't you get 3V at pin 13?
Check R7100.

"PP3V42_G3H 3.4 V"
Why don't you get 3.4V at pin 12V?
Check the trace.

"Pin 3 0v"
Fix ACIN problem too; check R7110.

title: 820-00165 MacBook Air 2017 water damage
message:
If R7100 is 0 ohm, why don't you get 3V at pin 13???

R7110 is 130K resistor.
It will measure lower onboard, but far of 480 ohm.
Post diode mode to ground at pin 3.

Please, try to understand a schematic!
